   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Math &amp; Science Education for South African Youth</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Umkhumbane Schools Project works in the 5 secondary schools in the Cato Manor township area near Durban, South Africa to give disadvantaged youth a chance at educational success and a brighter future.  As an NGO based on-site within a cluster of schools, we create opportunities for resource-sharing, collaboration, and friendly inter-school competition.  This Global Giving initiative will help fund our after-school classes, pre-college enrichment and mentoring, and teaching-resource center.</narrative>
  </description>
